62
00:04:42,410 --> 00:04:44,970
Who are you? Who are you?

63
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,940
You're not that bastard.

64
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:51,310
Who sent you?

65
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:59,820
Ha Tae Sik.

66
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,360
Ha Tae Sik.

67
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:15,720
Ha Tae Sik? Ha Tae Sik?

68
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:19,680
Where is it? Ha Tae Sik. Ha Tae Sik.

69
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:23,170
Joonggeon three-way intersection. Joonggeon three-way intersection.

70
00:05:23,170 --> 00:05:25,320
That's right. The three-way-intersection...

71
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,320
