No! No! You don't know!

105
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:27,970
You haven't been to hell!

106
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:30,580
Hell?

107
00:08:32,010 --> 00:08:33,920
Hell!

108
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:35,940
Dark and suffocating,

109
00:08:35,940 --> 00:08:39,670
repeated excruciating pain every day,

110
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:43,090
that damned hell!

111
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:47,750
I have been there too.

112
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:50,160
That hell.

113
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:54,290
You too? You came back alive from it, too?

114
00:08:54,290 --> 00:08:56,580
Like me?

115
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:03,310
I'm still there.

116
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:07,970
You are?

117
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:13,430
I resurrected.

118
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:16,390
I resurrected!

119
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:21,690
Tell me, Eom Soo Tak.

120
00:09:21,690 --> 00:09:24,740
How did you resurrect from that hell?

121
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:17,210
Ha Tae Sik told me about this place.

122
00:10:17,210 --> 00:10:19,440
He said I would be safe here.

123
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:22,810
He hid you here after you ran away?

124
00:10:25,090 --> 00:10:26,840
Did Ha Tae Sik really send you?

125
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:30,910
Then it's not safe here anymore!

126
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:33,730
4789! 4789! 4789!

127
00:10:33,730 --> 00:10:38,170
Devil! Devil! Devil bastard! Crazy bastard!

128
00:10:38,170 --> 00:10:41,030
Yellow color... Dol Ak. Dol Ak!

129
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:45,220
Dol Ak! I saw Dol Ak.

130
00:10:45,940 --> 00:10:48,920
Dol Ak. I can't talk about that.

131
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:52,120
4789 will protect me.

132
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:58,100
Eom Soo Tak, be quiet!

133
