Someone is coming.

134
00:11:10,830 --> 00:11:14,760

135
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:20,830
Hello, I'm from Mucheon Metropolitan Police Agency.

136
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:21,920
Oh okay.

137
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:25,210
I have a few questions to ask regarding a case we are investigating.

138
00:11:25,210 --> 00:11:29,510
Do the numbers 4789 ring a bell?

139
00:11:29,510 --> 00:11:32,370
It's a special suite at our hospital.

140
00:11:32,370 --> 00:11:34,530
A hospital room.

141
00:11:34,530 --> 00:11:36,870
What is the name of the admitted patient?

142
00:11:38,090 --> 00:11:42,020
It's that bastard. That bastard is coming.

143
00:11:42,850 --> 00:11:44,810
Be quiet.

144
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,360
Eom Soo Tak!

145
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:54,590
- Eom Soo Tak, what's wrong? Who are you?
- Doctor, Doctor!

146
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:56,300
Please help me. That bastard came.

147
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:59,200
- I understand, so please calm down.
- Doctor! Doctor, save me!

148
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:02,120
Calm down, okay? Wait just one moment.

149
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:04,480
Eom Soo Tak, please give me your arm.

150
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,420
Eom Soo Tak!

151
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:09,310
Calm down, please. Eom Soo Tak!

152
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:11,770
You're working with that bastard, aren't you?

153
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:16,060
Don't come any closer! I'll kill him.

154
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:18,120
This is the safest place for you.

155
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:21,560
That bastard has come. That bastard is here!

156
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:25,530
- Don't do something you'll regret. Come on. 
 - Stay back!

157
00:12:25,530 --> 00:12:28,660
Calm down, please. Eom Soo Tak!

158
00:12:39,770 --> 00:12:43,680
Eom Soo Tak. Eom Soo Tak!

159
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:45,400
Open the door, quickly!

160
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:48,280
Hurry! Hurry!

161
