♫  Confess your sins with blinks  ♫

547
00:56:04,990 --> 00:56:09,750
♫  Eyes you flicker  ♫

548
00:56:12,180 --> 00:56:19,910
♫  As though putting together fragmented traces  ♫

549
00:56:22,710 --> 00:56:32,210
♫  The memories which you have lost  ♫

550
00:56:32,210 --> 00:56:40,340
♫  You left me behind  ♫

551
00:56:40,340 --> 00:56:42,350
Detective Oh.

552
00:56:42,350 --> 00:56:46,940
♫  Who wandered alone searching for you  ♫

553
00:56:46,940 --> 00:56:49,380
This is that bastard's hideout.

554
00:56:54,890 --> 00:56:56,680
You finally found it.

555
00:56:56,680 --> 00:56:58,140
That's right.

556
00:56:58,140 --> 00:57:00,170
Have you contacted Team Leader yet?

557
00:57:00,170 --> 00:57:02,370
Not yet.

558
00:57:02,370 --> 00:57:05,110
Memorize using your photographic memory first.

559
00:57:49,600 --> 00:57:52,630
That doll isn't a victim's.

560
00:57:52,630 --> 00:57:54,250
It's definitely that bastard's.

561
00:57:54,250 --> 00:57:57,410
It must have some special meaning.

562
00:58:21,220 --> 00:58:23,310
This doll...

563
00:58:24,510 --> 00:58:26,690
I know it.

564
00:58:30,870 --> 00:58:36,360
Twenty years ago, in the car that hit my mom and ran,

565
00:58:36,360 --> 00:58:40,490
the child who was sitting in the back was holding this doll.

566
00:58:51,070 --> 00:58:54,270

567
00:59:10,110 --> 00:59:13,330
 Tell me one person whom you want to kill.

568
00:59:21,180 --> 00:59:23,390
 You did well.

569
00:59:36,300 --> 00:59:46,360

570
00:59:57,300 --> 01:00:00,070

571
01:00:00,070 --> 01:00:02,130
 Do you remember that doll?

572
01:00:02,130 --> 01:00:03,810
 What do you know that you came to see me?

573
01:00:03,810 --> 01:00:07,080
 For five years now, why must we continue to do something that makes us tremble?

574
01:00:07,080 --> 01:00:10,450
 I can't stand to see the organization I belong to falter.

575
01:00:10,450 --> 01:00:13,350
 Being predictable isn't his style.

576
01:00:13,350 --> 01:00:15,110
 We have to find his goal.

577
01:00:15,110 --> 01:00:19,280
 What's the evidence that Director Choi wants to hide?

578
01:00:19,990 --> 01:00:22,650
 What the hell is going on?

579
01:00:22,650 --> 01:00:25,240
 You weren't going to be able to catch him from the first place.

580
01:00:25,240 --> 01:00:29,110
 That bastard just cut off his tail, that's all.
